  "text": "Identified 10 core C++ source files implementing dynamic cluster discovery and health checking in Envoy:\n\n1. **CDS subscription**: `cds_api_impl.cc` implements `CdsApiImpl` which handles xDS config updates for cluster discovery via gRPC/REST subscriptions. `cds_api_helper.cc` provides `CdsApiHelper` for processing incremental CDS updates (added/removed clusters). `od_cds_api_impl.cc` implements on-demand CDS (`OdCdsApiImpl`) for lazy cluster fetching.\n\n2. **Cluster manager update logic**: `cluster_manager_impl.cc` contains `ClusterManagerImpl` with `addOrUpdateCluster()` and `removeCluster()` to apply CDS updates, plus `onClusterInit()` for post-initialization flow. `cluster_factory_impl.cc` contains `ClusterFactoryImplBase::create()` which wires up health checkers and outlier detection during cluster construction.\n\n3. **Active health check scheduling**: `health_checker_impl.cc` has `HealthCheckerFactory::create()` for constructing health checkers. `health_checker_base_impl.cc` has `HealthCheckerImplBase` and its nested `ActiveHealthCheckSession` which manages interval/timeout timers for scheduling periodic health checks.\n\n4. **Outlier detection integration**: `outlier_detection_impl.cc` implements `DetectorImpl` with ejection/unejection logic, consecutive error tracking, and success rate analysis. `upstream_impl.cc` contains `ClusterImplBase::setHealthChecker()` and `setOutlierDetector()` which wire health checking and outlier detection into the cluster. `health_discovery_service.cc` implements the HDS delegate for server-directed health checking.",
